org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionDecorator

  • 使用BeanDefinitionDecorator的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.beans.factory.xml
    Contains an abstract XML-based BeanFactory implementation, including a standard "spring-beans" XSD.

    • org.springframework.beans.factory.xml中BeanDefinitionDecorator的使用

      参数类型为BeanDefinitionDecorator的org.springframework.beans.factory.xml中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      protected void NamespaceHandlerSupport.registerBeanDefinitionDecorator(String elementName, BeanDefinitionDecorator dec)
      Subclasses can call this to register the supplied BeanDefinitionDecorator to handle the specified element.
      protected void NamespaceHandlerSupport.registerBeanDefinitionDecoratorForAttribute(String attrName, BeanDefinitionDecorator dec)
      Subclasses can call this to register the supplied BeanDefinitionDecorator to handle the specified attribute.
